      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from coupon testing of the same Ti-6Al-4V heat lot used in the construct specimens; geometric inputs from CMM measurements of production screws.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus (1.2 GPa) were measured from tensile coupons machined from the same billet as the test constructs. Screw and rod geometry was digitized via CMM with 5 μm tolerance. Input uncertainty propagated through the model; uval = 47 N for yield force QoI. Achieved level equals required level; criterion met."
    },
