      "rationale": "N=11 constructs were assembled using production screws and rods from the same lot. Dimensional inspection of all 11 constructs confirmed conformance to ±0.05 mm drawing tolerances. Sample size provides adequate statistical power for mean comparison at α=0.05. Achieved level equals required level; criterion met."
