      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Testing performed under at least two independent loading conditions or laboratories to bound test variability; inter-laboratory reproducibility documented.",
      "rationale": "Testing was conducted at two independent laboratories per ASTM F1717 protocol, providing inter-laboratory reproducibility data. However, only a single loading condition (static compression-bending at 5 mm/min) was evaluated; cyclic and off-axis conditions were not included. Achieved level (2) is below required level (3); this gap is acknowledged and bounded by the conservative acceptance criterion of <10% QoI difference.",
      "gapNarrative": "Single test condition limits generalizability; additional loading conditions are planned for the cannulated variant study."
