      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness: E/uval=0.81, 4.2%; yield force: E/uval=1.42, 6.7%; force at 40 mm: E/uval=1.03, 5.1%) satisfy both acceptance criteria. Comparison was performed against the experimental mean ± 95% CI across N=11 constructs at both laboratories. Achieved level equals required level; criterion met."
    },
    {
